PrecisOrder (a) setting apart some 949 hectares of land in Saskatchewan, mines and minerals included, for the use and benefit of the OCHAPOWACE INDIAN BAND as Ochapowace Indian Reserves Nos. 71-23, 71-24, 71-25, 71-26, 71-37, 71-38, 71-39 and 71-40, and (b) consenting to the exercise by TRANSGAS LIMITED and SASKATCHEWAN POWER CORPORATION of their powers to expropriate land or any interest therein.
